name: Sakura Miku
description: Sakura Miku is the name of a Hatsune Miku Japanese Vocaloid module. Sakura Miku is a pink-themed alternate hue for Hatsune Miku, designed to symbolize the start of spring. The official Sakura Miku appeared in 2011. At the 2011 Hatsune Miku concert, a small Sakura Miku of about 3.5cm was given away. The "Project DIVA" series includes Sakura Miku as an alternate character module for Hatsune Miku.
